title.rendered: Day 1 – Mister Triple X. Miami Swim Week

content.rendered:
Miami Swim Week Powered by Art Hearts Fashion Day 1. 

24Fashion TV Exclusive:

Mister Triple X

Fan favorite, Mister Triple X, helmed by Art Hearts Fashion founder Erik Rosete, pumped up the energy this season with camo and floral prints, bright pops of color, and metallic harnesses. His work is tasteful and provocative, sexy and hot, all in at the same time. The collection was well-received by the audience that filled the Faena Forum to capacity. Male models wore clean, modern footwear by Vagary Worldwide.

Fashion model Cameron Clark walks for Mister Triple X

Fashion model Grant Bradley walks for Mister Triple X

Fashion model Gonzalo Calzon walks for Mister Triple X

Fashion model Anastasia Nova walks for Mister Triple X

Fashion models and twins Gemelos Castillo walk for Mister Triple X

Mikeya Cesheridan walks for Mister Triple X

Fashion model Monique Victoria walks for Mister Triple X

Fashion model Wyatt Engeman walks for Mister Triple X
